title: ダイヤモンドSの後に・準備は万全！

text_block_list.text: Matikanetannhauser gave it her all in the 'Diamond S'!
Matikanetannhauser's public reputation is on the rise. The stands showed more excitement than expected, and the race came to a close.
Meanwhile, in front of the racecourse. The round-glasses reporter from earlier finally gets transferred from the Umamusume department, which was just starting to heat up, to another department...
Matikanetannhauser knows nothing of this. She's full of fighting spirit and has gained considerable skill! Next up is the Tenno Sho (Spring)'...!
